Description: You have Mastery over Primal Forces and energy to blast your foes, increase your power, and to add some much needed armor and defense.

Powers.DescShort: Melee, Extreme DMG(Energy/Smash), Foe Disorient, Self -HP
Powers.DescLong: Mastery of Energy Melee begins with the ability to transfer your own Hit Points into a punch that deals extreme damage. Energy Transfer has a good chance of Disorienting the target. Damage: Extreme, Recharge: Slow
You can focus for a moment to conserve your Endurance. After activating this power, you expend less Endurance on all other powers for a while. Recharge: Very Long

Energy Torrent unleashes a cone of powerful energy that can smash foes and possibly send them flying. You must be level 41 and have Energy Transfer or Conserve Power before selecting this power.  Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Slow
When you toggle on this power, you become highly resistant to Smashing and Lethal damage. You must be level 41 and have Energy Transfer or Conserve Power before selecting this power. Recharge: Fast

Powers.DescShort: Ranged (Targeted AoE), Moderate DMG(Smash/Energy), Foe Knockback
Powers.DescLong: You hurl a blast of charged energy that violently explodes on impact, damaging all foes near the target. Explosive Blast may knock targets backwards. You must be level 44 and have two other Primal Forces Mastery Powers before selecting this power. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Slow
